latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Thank you ❤️🙏🏼
It has been such a wonderful journey these past four months. Participating in Dancing Stars Nepal has definitely been the highlight of my 2022. 🤗❤️🍀 I am grateful for the life I have. And will definitely continue to dance since I fell in love with it. No matter who the winner is tonight I thank each and everyone who have supported us and loved us so much. My heart and soul is so happy. Thank you 🙏🏼❤️🍀✨ #journey #dancingstarsnepal

Can’t express enough how much I love dancing Latin dance forms. 😍❤️✨💃🏻 Performed Flamenco for the first time in my life ever and honestly I wasn’t expecting full 30/30 marks from the judges. Was so overwhelmed and started crying happy tears. 🥲 Such an experience it was! The task was to dance alone without our choreographers. Also made it to top 4 yaaay 🎊🥳 Please do continue to support us team “ParaJD” by downloading the Khalti app and khalti.com for those who are abroad for us to make it to top 3. 🤗❤️🍀✨🥳🎊 My beautiful flamenco outfit by @aaroops_design ❤️✨ #dancingstarsnepal

I wrote “Andhakar” when I was at one of the most lowest point in my life during lockdown. Getting an opportunity to perform on my own song at Dancing Stars Nepal advocating about mental health has been the most special episode till now for me. Just couldn’t hold back my emotions on this one. 🖤 
Those who are going through the hardest times in life, always remember you are not alone. You matter and are loved so so much. I love you ❤️
And thank you so much my choreographer JD @jd_tamu for creating this piece which I will cherish and appreciate it forever. 🙏🏼❤️✨ Special thank you to @manikrai39 @renukaghartimagar @ramchandra.paneru & @slumgang.roshangahatraj for being a part of this. 🤗❤️✨🍀

Thank you @yumi_balami for joining us in yesterday’s performance. 😍❤️✨ Had so much fun performing on this song Fasiyo by @vjmusic 🍀 Please keep voting for us downloading the @khaltiofficial app and those who are abroad can vote from khalti.com Thank you so much for all the love and support till now. Forever grateful 🍀❤️✨🙏🏼🥳

By far this is the best performance I’ve given and I’m so grateful for the results. 🙏🏼❤️🍀✨ Yet another 30/30 performance by team “ParaJD” on Dancing Stars Nepal 🌟I am so much in love with Latin dance forms. 😍 And the dance form we did “Paso Doble” will always be close to my heart. ❤️✨Thank you so much my dance partner @jd_tamu Our costume designer @aaroops_design 🙏🏼❤️✨ Also please don’t forget to vote for team “ParaJD” downloading the Khalti app. It’s double elimination tonight so need your love and support as always. 🍀✨ For international voting please go to khalti.com. Thank you 🤗❤️🙏🏼🍀✨ #grateful #dancingstarsnepal #dance #pasodoble #pasodoblecostume #parajd #realitydanceshow

This episode of Dancing Stars Nepal was very special for me because it was a family member special. Got the opportunity to welcome my mother on the stage and it meant so much to me. ❤️✨🍀 Thank you so much @slumgang.roshangahatraj for being my dance partner while @jd_tamu was unwell. Truly appreciate it. 🤗✨ Also this Saturday is double elimination so please don’t forget to vote for team “ParaJD” on Khalti app. We are at lucky number 07 🍀❤️🌟✨ those who are abroad can also vote for us on khalti.com 💐 Thank you so much for the love and support you all have given us till now. Truly grateful from the whole of my heart and soul. ❤️✨🌟 Also special thank you to @alkas.atelier for our dance costume this week. ❤️✨

Yesterday, I took a big step toward healing for the little girl inside me who has waited so long to be seen, heard, and held. 🕊️✨
I went for an inner child healing session with the lovely @o_mindyourbody at @primordiall_waters and it was truly transformative. Surrounded by calming energy, crystals, and kindness, I released so much I didn’t even know I was holding in. 🥹✨

It brought me clarity, softness, and a deep reminder: I deserve to live a happy, successful, and full life and it begins with healing myself first. 🌱💫

If you’ve ever felt lost, stuck, or weighed down by your past, I truly recommend experiencing this kind of inner work at least once in your life. It’s powerful. It’s freeing. It’s beautiful. 💛

Here’s to becoming the best version of myself not just for the world, but for me.
Special thanks to @maisoncreative.in ❤️✨🍀

She followed me not too close, not too far.
Just enough to let me know “I see you.”
When I turned around,
she pretended not to care 
sniffing the ground, looking away,
as if to say “Oh, me? I was just passing by.”

Shy. Gentle. So full of soul.
In that quiet little dance of trust,
my heart felt whole.

It’s moments like these 
unplanned, unsaid,
but deeply felt 
that remind me why I love this world.

And yes I fed her.
With food, and love, and a silent promise
that she was seen. 🐾❤️✨

#momentsthatmatter #thelittlethingsinlife #thisislove

latestPosts.caption:
This was a real hit to my confidence and I don’t want anyone else to go through it. ❤️‍🩹

I’ve always had people admire my skin it became a part of how I saw myself. 🪞
But after using a face razor straight from the packet (without disinfecting it), I developed contact dermatitis.
Painful, itchy, inflamed and honestly, heartbreaking.

It wasn’t just about skin it shook my self confidence.

So please… Always disinfect your facial razor.
Use rubbing alcohol or soak it in hot water for 15-20 minutes before you let it touch your skin.
It’s such a small step that can save you so much heartache.

What helped me heal?
	•	Cetaphil DAM Moisturizer
	•	Akind Sunscreen (both derm approved)
 (And of course antibiotics, steroid tablets,  medicated face cream & drinking loads of water)

Gentle, effective these two honestly saved my skin.
And yes, both are available on @tirabeauty Beauty if you need them.

I hope this video helps someone out there. 💙
Be careful. Your skin deserves the love and protection.

And that’s exactly what @jacksonwang852g7 poured into Magic Man 2. 🍀

I have nothing but deep respect, love, and appreciation for the way Jackson shares his most authentic self with the world.
This album isn’t just music… it’s a piece of his heart and all the experiences he has faced in life till now. 
I found myself sobbing while listening wanting nothing more than to give Jackson a long, healing hug. 🥹🫂🫶🏻

Magic Man 2 is a masterpiece… thank you to Jackson and every soul behind this creation for giving us something so real and soul stirring.

If you haven’t already please listen to Jackson Wang’s latest album Magic Man 2.
You’ll feel every word, every note from the heart. ❤️✨

latestPosts.caption:
After moons of longing, she crossed the miles,
With hydrangeas cradled in trembling hands,
A heart stitched with hope, eyes lit with yearning,
Searching the crowd for the face she called home.

And there
Not a dream, nor a cruel mirage,
But him…
With another.

The colors drained from her waiting world,
Disbelief a silent gasp inside her soul,
Then shock like glass shattering in her veins,
Then grief wild, merciless, flooding like a river.

She stood afar, a shadow swallowed by the crowd,
Hands pressed against the wreckage of her chest,
Watching love kiss lies beneath a stranger’s gaze.

Her tears fell not for him,
But for the foolish heart that dared to hope.

Disgust curled in her throat like unshed words,
For she had come to offer flowers,
And left with the ashes of her pride.
- Paramita Rana.
